channel.title: Webclient help trying to put webclient on webs
channel.description:
hey guys, im trying to put a webclient on webs but saddly its not working im sure its not from the cache because the ( client.jar ) i made downloads the cache for ppl who dont have it so it must mean that it works cuz it downloaded it for few of my friends... but when i upload the client to my (webs) website and put the HTML code for webclient it doesnt work it gets stuck at the beginning (loading) and nothing else just stays looking like that for 20minutes.. and ill post the HTML webclient code below so you all can check it thanks alot.
<TITLE>project dice WEBCLIENT</TITLE> <META HTTP-EQUIV="PRAGMA" CONTENT="NO-CACHE"> </HEAD>
<BODY>
<applet name="project-dice v3.5" width="765" height="503" archive="client.jar" code="client.class"> <param name="java_arguments" value="-Xmx1024m"> </applet>
To Download the desktop client please use this link: ( http://uppit.com/taqoqf8iuzgr/client.jar ) Download the cache from www.projectdicersps.webs.com(projectdice v3.5).zip and extract it to C:/ and reload this page!
</BODY> </HTML> </BODY> </HTML>
